<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 04:07:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>英国气候变化大臣格雷厄姆·斯图尔特辞职</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-climate-change-minister-graham-stuart-resigns/articleshow/109260701.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109260701.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国气候变化大臣格雷厄姆·斯图尔特在任职八年后辞去政府职务，称辞职时机已到。由于工党在民意调查中领先，斯图尔特计划与首相里希·苏纳克的保守党一起竞选连任。贾斯汀·汤姆林森接替斯图尔特担任气候部长，承认斯图尔特对清洁能源转型的贡献。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 02:19:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-climate-change-minister-graham-stuart-resigns/articleshow/109260701.cms</guid></item><item><title>无政府状态的海地终于成立过渡统治委员会</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/transitional-ruling-council-finally-forms-in-anarchic-haiti/articleshow/109260249.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109260249.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;星期五，这个加勒比国家正式成立了一个管理委员会，其任务是填补海地的领导真空并恢复表面上的秩序，该国因帮派暴力的爆发而震动。该法令要求理事会“迅速”任命新总理和“包容”海地各政治派别的政府。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 00:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/transitional-ruling-council-finally-forms-in-anarchic-haiti/articleshow/109260249.cms</guid></item><item><title>关注中国：乔·拜登誓言保卫日本和菲律宾</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/eye-on-china-joe-biden-vows-to-defend-japan-philippines/articleshow/109260067.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109260067.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统拜登重申了对日本和菲律宾的防务承诺，警告不要在南中国海发动袭击。北京为其行为辩护，反对干涉集团政治和损害战略利益的行为。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 00:00:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/eye-on-china-joe-biden-vows-to-defend-japan-philippines/articleshow/109260067.cms</guid></item><item><title>反军政府部队占领缅甸主要贸易城镇，反攻迫在眉睫</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/anti-junta-forces-take-key-trading-town-in-myanmar-counteroffensive-looms/articleshow/109260019.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109260019.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;抵抗力量占领了泰国边境的重要城镇妙瓦迪，影响了与缅甸的贸易。随着政权计划反攻，数千人逃离。泰国担心边境暴力，主动提出调解冲突。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 23:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/anti-junta-forces-take-key-trading-town-in-myanmar-counteroffensive-looms/articleshow/109260019.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国向海外提供的援助减少，而用于收容难民的预算却相同</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-sending-less-aid-overseas-as-same-budget-used-to-fund-hosting-refugees/articleshow/109259944.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109259944.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 2023年，英国将三分之一的援助预算用于收容英国境内的难民，导致发展中国家的资金紧张。对较贫穷国家的双边援助减少，特别是在亚洲，影响了全球支持举措和人道主义援助工作。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 23:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-sending-less-aid-overseas-as-same-budget-used-to-fund-hosting-refugees/articleshow/109259944.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙家庭 60 多名成员在以色列多次袭击中丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/over-60-members-of-gaza-family-killed-in-separate-israeli-strikes/articleshow/109259784.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109259784.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙的塔巴蒂比家庭面临一个月内的第二场悲剧，60 多名亲属在以色列轰炸中丧生。建筑物遭到罢工，造成 25 人死亡，而在准备斋月餐食期间又造成 36 人死亡。随着损失的加深，家人陷入哀悼。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 23:35:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/over-60-members-of-gaza-family-killed-in-separate-israeli-strikes/articleshow/109259784.cms</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫高级将领对驻以色列美军人员实施旅行限制</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/travel-curbs-on-us-personnel-in-israel-top-general-in-tel-aviv/articleshow/109259701.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109259701.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于伊朗的潜在威胁，美国发布了以色列旅行指南。预计伊朗将发动重大袭击。英国建议公民离开。法国从伊朗撤离外交官家属。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 23:30:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/travel-curbs-on-us-personnel-in-israel-top-general-in-tel-aviv/articleshow/109259701.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列准备在 48 小时内应对伊朗的潜在袭击：报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-bracing-for-potential-attack-from-iran-within-48-hours-report/articleshow/109259649.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109259649.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列为伊朗可能袭击政府目标做好准备。开斋节后紧张局势升级。美国做好防御准备。外交努力加大。报复行动有待德黑兰批准。阿亚图拉阿里·哈梅内伊誓言惩罚以色列。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 23:26:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-bracing-for-potential-attack-from-iran-within-48-hours-report/articleshow/109259649.cms</guid></item><item><title>爱尔兰新总理表示距离承认巴勒斯坦国“更近了”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/new-irish-pm-says-getting-much-closer-to-recognising-palestinian-state/articleshow/109255552.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109255552.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 17:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/new-irish-pm-says-getting-much-closer-to-recognising-palestinian-state/articleshow/109255552.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国称地中海船只倾覆 45 名移民失踪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/un-says-45-migrants-missing-after-boat-capsizes-in-mediterranean/articleshow/109255465.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109255465.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;意大利海岸警卫队周三表示，在另一起沉船事故中，已发现 9 具遇难者尸体，并救起 22 人，其中 15 人疑似失踪。幸存者被带到附近的意大利兰佩杜萨岛，这是许多寻求到达欧盟的移民的第一个停靠港。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 17:42:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/un-says-45-migrants-missing-after-boat-capsizes-in-mediterranean/articleshow/109255465.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯因部长“不可接受”言论召见法国大使</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-summons-french-ambassador-over-ministers-unacceptable-comments/articleshow/109255410.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109255410.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 17:39:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-summons-french-ambassador-over-ministers-unacceptable-comments/articleshow/109255410.cms</guid></item><item><title>研究显示，到 2050 年，日本独居老年人口将增加 47%</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japans-elderly-population-living-alone-to-jump-47-by-2050-research/articleshow/109254665.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109254665.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:46:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japans-elderly-population-living-alone-to-jump-47-by-2050-research/articleshow/109254665.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击威胁使该地区紧张，以色列袭击加沙</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-pounds-gaza-as-iran-attack-threat-puts-region-on-edge/articleshow/109254496.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109254496.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;居民报告周五以色列在加沙中部猛烈开火，伊朗威胁要对本月在叙利亚发动的袭击造成两名伊朗将军死亡，导致地区紧张局势加剧。哈马斯统治地区当局报告称，加沙中部地区发生了数十次新的空袭。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-pounds-gaza-as-iran-attack-threat-puts-region-on-edge/articleshow/109254496.cms</guid></item><item><title>白宫称伊朗对以色列的威胁“真实”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-threat-to-israel-real-says-white-house/articleshow/109253312.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109253312.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;白宫承认伊朗在叙利亚袭击后对以色列发出威胁。柯比确保防御准备状态。阿亚图拉发誓要进行惩罚，内塔尼亚胡则表示已做好准备。德黑兰批评联合国保持沉默，内塔尼亚胡誓言进行报复。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:19:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-threat-to-israel-real-says-white-house/articleshow/109253312.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙家庭 60 多名成员在以色列多次袭击中丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/over-60-members-of-gaza-family-killed-in-separate-israeli-strikes/articleshow/109253253.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109253253.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙的塔巴蒂比一家在不到一个月的时间里第二次陷入哀悼，此前以色列对他们避难的建筑物进行了多次轰炸，造成 60 多名亲属死亡。 - “我们在里面时”房屋遭到轰炸 - 塔巴蒂比一家多次因以色列的轰炸而流离失所，他们已经陷入了哀悼之中。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:05:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/over-60-members-of-gaza-family-killed-in-separate-israeli-strikes/articleshow/109253253.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国专家谴责巴基斯坦强迫婚姻和少数群体改变宗教信仰</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/un-experts-condemn-forced-marriages-religious-conversions-of-minorities-in-pakistan/articleshow/109252208.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109252208.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国专家周四表示，巴基斯坦宗教少数群体的妇女和儿童很容易遭受强迫宗教皈依和婚姻，以及性侵犯和贩运。声明还敦促巴基斯坦当局平等对待所有妇女，包括来自“印度教和基督教”社区的妇女。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 14:39:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/un-experts-condemn-forced-marriages-religious-conversions-of-minorities-in-pakistan/articleshow/109252208.cms</guid></item><item><title>意大利将在黎巴嫩、科特迪瓦和埃塞俄比亚招募移民工人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/italy-to-recruit-migrant-workers-in-lebanon-ivory-coast-and-ethiopia/articleshow/109254388.cms</link><description>意大利同意通过天主教慈善机构圣艾智德社区牵头的一项特别倡议，欢迎来自黎巴嫩、科特迪瓦和埃塞俄比亚的 300 名移民工人。这些人不会获得难民身份，但将成为名为“工作走廊”的试点项目的一部分。这项倡议得到了内政部的批准，符合总理乔治亚·梅洛尼政府的立场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:24:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/italy-to-recruit-migrant-workers-in-lebanon-ivory-coast-and-ethiopia/articleshow/109254388.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国外交部将巴基斯坦列入“太危险而不能旅行”的国家名单</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/uk-foreign-office-adds-pakistan-to-its-list-of-countries-too-dangerous-to-travel/articleshow/109252405.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109252405.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国外交、联邦与发展办公室（FCDO）最近将巴基斯坦添加到其国家名单中，称其对英国公民来说“太危险”而不能旅行。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 14:19:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/uk-foreign-office-adds-pakistan-to-its-list-of-countries-too-dangerous-to-travel/articleshow/109252405.cms</guid></item><item><title>庞贝城发现隐藏了 2000 年的引人注目的画作</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hidden-for-2000-years-striking-paintings-uncovered-in-pompeii/articleshow/109247650.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109247650.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;庞贝城最近的发掘发现了一个宴会厅，里面有神话壁画，包括阿波罗引诱卡桑德拉和特洛伊的海伦与巴黎会面的壁画。这个保存完好的遗址还设有面包店和马赛克地板，让您可以深入了解古罗马生活。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 11:14:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/hidden-for-2000-years-striking-paintings-uncovered-in-pompeii/articleshow/109247650.cms</guid></item><item><title>“不需要手机信号塔：中国彻底改变了智能手机通信”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/no-need-for-cell-towers-china-has-revolutionised-smartphone-communications/articleshow/109246416.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109246416.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国科学家实现了突破性的里程碑，世界上第一颗卫星“天通”实现了智能手机直接通话。地球同步轨道天通一号系列覆盖亚太地区，支持华为、小米、荣耀、OPPO等品牌。卫星呼叫对于甘肃地震等紧急情况至关重要。中国在卫星通信领域处于领先地位，缩小了全球通信差距。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 10:33:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/no-need-for-cell-towers-china-has-revolutionised-smartphone-communications/articleshow/109246416.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>